NK019(dza)001:5605: pa'i cho ga rtsa rgyud kyi rdo rje rnal 'byor
NK019(dza)001:5606: 'jug pa'i le'u las bshad pa ltar ram /
NK019(dza)001:5607: dgongs 'dus kyi ru dra dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i cho ga gnyis gang rung gis bcug la /
NK019(dza)001:5608: dgongs 'dus kyi le'u bdun cu pa dang /
NK019(dza)001:5609: bcu gsum pa gnyis kyis spyi khog dbub cing /
NK019(dza)001:5610: ji ltar bskur ba'i cho ga rtsa rgyud kyi rdo
NK019(dza)001:5611: rje dbang gi le'u las bshad pa ltar gyis chu
NK019(dza)001:5612: bo bzhi rdzogs su bskur bar gsungs pa yin no
NK019(dza)001:5613: // 'dir rtsa rgyud kyi dpe rgyun phal mo cher /
NK019(dza)001:5614: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub lugs le'u bcu bzhi par
NK019(dza)001:5615: snang bas lung bstan ma'i 'grel tshig 'di dang 'gal
NK019(dza)001:5616: lo snyam na / de ni 'grel pa so so'i
NK019(dza)001:5617: dgongs pas rgyud kyi le'u'i gcod mtshams tha dad par
NK019(dza)001:5619: dper na 'grel chung du rtsa rgyud kyi rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK019(dza)001:5620: rdo rje mchog chen gyi le'u gnyis so sor phye ba dang /
NK019(dza)001:5621: rgyud rang gi glegs bam phal che bar /
NK019(dza)001:5622: 'jug pa dang dbang le'u so lnga pa dang so drug par byas te /
NK019(dza)001:5623: spyir rgyud la le'u so bdun du phye yang /
NK019(dza)001:5624: rgya mdud 'grel du spyir le'u so drug tu bsdus nas /
NK019(dza)001:5625: 'jug pa dang dbang so bzhi so lnga gnyis la snang zhing /
NK019(dza)001:5626: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub lugs kyang le'u bcu gnyis
NK019(dza)001:5627: pa rang la yod pas lung bstan ma'i 'grel tshig
NK019(dza)001:5628: 'di yig nor ro snyam du bsam par mi bya'o
NK019(dza)001:5630: gsang bdag chen po sgro phug pas mdzad pa'i gsang
NK019(dza)001:5631: sngags lung gi 'dus pa mdo'i dbang gi mdzad byang
NK019(dza)001:5632: zhes par / zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor tshogs chen 'dus pa thun mong ba'i lugs su bzhengs nas /
NK019(dza)001:5633: der sngar ltar 'jug pa dang dbang so drug rtsa rgyud bzhin du rdzogs par bskur tshul gsungs shing /
NK019(dza)001:5634: dbang chog 'di ni rgyud lugs kyi mdo dbang nyung
NK019(dza)001:5635: gsal rdzogs pa'i yig cha ngo mtshar can du snang
NK019(dza)001:5636: mod / de lta na'ang ha cang tshig sna thung bas ma khrol ba yin nam /
NK019(dza)001:5637: phyis kyi gang zag rnams kyis ni spangs pa lta bur gyur to //
NK019(dza)001:5638: de ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gnyis gang rung du
NK019(dza)001:5639: mdo dbang dngos sum cu rtsa drug rdzogs par bskur
NK019(dza)001:5641: 'dus pa mdo'i rgyud rtsa bshad kyis dngos bstan ltar
NK019(dza)001:5642: gyi mdo'i dbang thun mong ma yin par snang bas
NK019(dza)001:5643: / gtso che ba'i ngos nas rgyud lugs zhes bya zhing /
NK019(dza)001:5644: bde ba gsal mdzad kyis dbang don rnam par 'byed
NK019(dza)001:5645: par rjes 'jug las dang po la chu bo bzhi
NK019(dza)001:5646: bskur tshul bshad pa'i man ngag dang yang 'brel te
NK019(dza)001:5647: / rang bzhin gyis snod du gyur pa'i skal ldan
NK019(dza)001:5648: gyi slob ma khyad par can rnams la bskur bya'i
NK019(dza)001:5649: / dbang yin no // gsum pa rtsa dkyil gnyis
NK019(dza)001:5650: gang rung du ji ltar bskur ba'i cho ga'i khyad
NK019(dza)001:5653: gzhi dang gzhung gis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK019(dza)001:5654: phun sum tshogs pa lnga gzhi la //
NK019(dza)001:5655: bsnyen sgrub bzhi yis gzhung bsrang ba'ang //
NK019(dza)001:5657: sgrub pa'i gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK019(dza)001:5658: sgrub pa'i gzhung srong zhing dbang bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:5660: gang gis sgrub pa'i ston pa rdo rje rgyal po /
NK019(dza)001:5661: gang dang lhan cig sgrub pa'i 'khor /
NK019(dza)001:5663: gang la brten nas sgrub pa'i yo byad /
NK019(dza)001:5664: gang gi tshe sgrub pa'i dus so //
NK019(dza)001:5667: bla ma rdo rje 'khor lo rgyal //
NK019(dza)001:5668: yon tan mchog gi gter gyur cing //
NK019(dza)001:5669: srid par zhus kyang zad mi shes //
NK019(dza)001:5670: rkyen thub dbang lung rdzogs pa bzung //
NK019(dza)001:5671: zhes pas lta sgom spyod gsum rnam par dag pas yon tan mchog gi gter du gyur cing /
NK019(dza)001:5672: lung rigs man ngag kun la mkhas pas mkhyen pa zad mi shes pa /
NK019(dza)001:5673: dbang lung man ngag rdzogs shing dam tshig gtsang bas gsang gnyer thub pa /
NK019(dza)001:5674: bshad sgrub rkyen khar mi gtong ba'i gzhan rjes su 'dzin pa'i thabs mkhas thugs rjer ldan pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:5676: sngar bstan pa ltar spyir slob ma'i snod kyi yon tan rnams tshang zhing /
NK019(dza)001:5679: rdo rje can gyi gzungs 'dzin ma //
NK019(dza)001:5681: 'chad mkhas pa'i rdo rje rgyal theb /
NK019(dza)001:5682: sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa'i gzungs ma /
NK019(dza)001:5683: dpa' brtul che ba'i kang+ki ra /
NK019(dza)001:5684: drod 'dzin pa'i rdo rje bya rog /
NK019(dza)001:5685: mthong bzlog nus pa'i rdo rje spyan pa /
NK019(dza)001:5686: skad gdangs snyan zhing las khrigs byang ba'i rdo rje las mkhan /
NK019(dza)001:5687: g.yos mkhas shing kha ska ba'i rdo rje byan po /
NK019(dza)001:5688: phyi nang brda sbyor mkhas pa'i rdo rje rdul phyags
NK019(dza)001:5689: sogs dngos shugs ci rigs pas tshom bur 'brel ba'i
NK019(dza)001:5692: sgrub pa'i gnas mchog dam pa dag /
NK019(dza)001:5693: skyon yon gnyis kyi bye brag ni //
NK019(dza)001:5694: nges par brtags te shes pa las //
NK019(dza)001:5695: blang dor gnyis su sbyar bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:5697: yi dwags gdugs pa can gyi 'gyu srang dang dgra rkun gcan gzan sogs kyis 'tshe ba med cing /
NK019(dza)001:5698: ston pa'i zhabs kyis bcags pas byin che ba /
NK019(dza)001:5699: rig 'dzin gong ma rnams kyis grub pa brnyes pas bkra shis pa /
NK019(dza)001:5700: gnam sa bar snang gi dpyad legs pas nyams dga' zhing yid du 'ong ba /
NK019(dza)001:5701: khyad par gzhung dang mthun pas sgrub thag nye ba
NK019(dza)001:5702: sogs bkra shis dge mtshan dang ldan pa'i gnas su
NK019(dza)001:5703: sgrub khang sum thog khor khang rim pa gsum pa
NK019(dza)001:5704: gnod pa zhi ba'i rdzas kyis byugs pa 'du bya
NK019(dza)001:5706: ri bo 'dus pa'i rtse rnams dang //
NK019(dza)001:5707: tsan+dana nags tshal me tog tshal //
NK019(dza)001:5708: yid 'ong bkra shis nyams dga' ba'i //
NK019(dza)001:5709: gnas su dkyil 'khor bri bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:5710: gnam dang sa dang bar snang rnams //
NK019(dza)001:5711: legs par brtags te las rnams bya //
NK019(dza)001:5714: rnyed nas tshom bu'i grangs bzhin du //
NK019(dza)001:5715: che chung rkyen du 'tshams par bya //
NK019(dza)001:5716: khor khang phyi nang bar ldan par //
NK019(dza)001:5717: rin chen byug pas bsrung ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:5718: rin chen sprul pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK019(dza)001:5719: yid 'ong bya ba shin tu gces //
NK019(dza)001:5723: der ni yod byad phun sum tshogs //
NK019(dza)001:5724: ci 'dod bltas te ma thogs par //
NK019(dza)001:5725: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar lnga las /
NK019(dza)001:5726: sgrub rdzas gsang ba'i yo byad ni /
NK019(dza)001:5727: thod sku sogs sgrub pa'i rten gsum byin can dang /
NK019(dza)001:5728: rmad du byung ba'i dam rdzas bam gtsang ma sogs
NK019(dza)001:5729: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rdzas dang dbang gi rdzas thun
NK019(dza)001:5730: mong ma yin pa rnams so //
NK019(dza)001:5731: mchod rdzas dag pa'i yo byad ni /
NK019(dza)001:5735: sgrub khang dang dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan gyi khyad par la sogs pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:5736: bar gcod rkyen bzlog gi yo byad ni /
NK019(dza)001:5737: nad sel ba'i sman dang sman pa /
NK019(dza)001:5739: bgegs bzlog gi nyul le skrod pa'i brab bdug gi rdzas la sogs pa rnams so //
NK019(dza)001:5740: 'tsho ba nyer mkho'i yo byad ni /
NK019(dza)001:5741: gos stan bza' btung sogs ma 'grub na spogs chog dgos pa'i phyir ldab ldang du gsog pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:5742: dgos pa mchog gi yo byad ni /
NK019(dza)001:5743: nyams len la the tshom gcod pa'i spyi dang khyad
NK019(dza)001:5744: par gyi rgyud lung man ngag rnams tshang bar 'du
NK019(dza)001:5745: bya zhing / lhag pa'i yo byad lnga la rang byan tshud pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:5747: spyir dbyar dgun ston dpyid kyi dus cha bzhi'i dang po ste ra ba bzhi dang /
NK019(dza)001:5748: bye brag tu nyi ma 'phel ba'i dus byang bgrod /
NK019(dza)001:5749: zla ba 'phel ba'i dus yar ngo /
NK019(dza)001:5750: de'i nang nas kyang tshes grangs brgyad nas bco lnga'i bar la /
NK019(dza)001:5751: rgyal phur 'dzom pa lta bu'i gza' skar sbyor byed
NK019(dza)001:5752: bzang po nas sgrub pa'i 'go rtsom pa shis pa
NK019(dza)001:5754: 'di ltar sbyar ba'i dus chen yang //
NK019(dza)001:5755: nges par brtags te mdo bzung la //
NK019(dza)001:5756: rig byed dag gi yan lag las //
NK019(dza)001:5757: shes par bya ste legs sbyar ba //
NK019(dza)001:5758: bkra shis lha yi nyi ma dang //
NK019(dza)001:5759: sbyor dang dus tshigs bzang po rnams //
NK019(dza)001:5760: 'jig rten mtshan ma'i rtog pa ste //
NK019(dza)001:5761: brtags na bkra shis mtshan ma 'byung //
NK019(dza)001:5764: dus ni dbyar dgun ston dpyid kyi //
NK019(dza)001:5765: ra ba dag la rab tu shis //
NK019(dza)001:5766: brgyad nas nya yi bar la gtad //
NK019(dza)001:5767: bkra shis gza' skar shis pa blang //
NK019(dza)001:5771: tshes grangs gza' ni dam par ldan //
NK019(dza)001:5772: phur bu pa sangs zla ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:5773: gza' lhag mchog gi las kun la //
NK019(dza)001:5774: gza' mchog 'di dag rtag tu ni //
NK019(dza)001:5775: bzhi pa tshes dang ldan pa ni //
NK019(dza)001:5776: sa steng 'jig rten kun tu ni //
NK019(dza)001:5779: tha skar snar ma nyid dang ni //
NK019(dza)001:5780: rgyal dang khrums ni stod smad gnyis //
NK019(dza)001:5781: nam gru dang ni lha mtshams dag /
NK019(dza)001:5782: bzlas pa'i dus su rab tu basngagasa //
NK019(dza)001:5784: grub pa'i don yang ster bar byed //
NK019(dza)001:5785: skar ma dag ni 'di dag la //
NK019(dza)001:5786: dkyil 'khor nyid kyang bri bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:5788: gzhan yang rtsa rgyud du dbyar ston dgun dpyid kyi
NK019(dza)001:5789: ra ba bzhi po rim par zhi rgyas dbang drag
NK019(dza)001:5790: gi las so so sgrub pa la shis par bstan
NK019(dza)001:5791: pa dang / bam rnyed pa'am gzungs ma 'du bya dang /
NK019(dza)001:5792: bslab bcu mthar phyin cing sgrol ba'i tshad la babs na'ang dus yin par gsungs so //
NK019(dza)001:5793: yang sgrub pa ji tsam byed pa'i dus ni /
NK019(dza)001:5794: smin slob kyi dbang du byas na //
NK019(dza)001:5795: zla ba drug dang lo gcig la sogs pa dngos
NK019(dza)001:5796: grub kyi mtshan ma gtan la ma phebs kyi bar
NK019(dza)001:5799: lo'am zla ba'i grangs bzhin du //
NK019(dza)001:5800: thabs dang cho gar ldan spyod pas //
NK019(dza)001:5801: zag med snang ba'i lam la gnas //
NK019(dza)001:5802: skye 'jig med pa'i skur gyur te //
NK019(dza)001:5803: bskal pa grangs med tshe la dbang //
NK019(dza)001:5804: bden pa'i don mthong 'jigs pa med //
NK019(dza)001:5806: mos slob la ni zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig gam
NK019(dza)001:5807: zhag bcu gcig lta bu la bsnyen sgrub yan lag
NK019(dza)001:5808: bzhi tshang bar nyams su len pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:5809: khyad par dbang bskur ba'i dus ni /
NK019(dza)001:5810: bsnyen sgrub rdzogs nas lhag pa'i sems skyes pa'i dus te /
NK019(dza)001:5812: dang po sems bskyed 'jug dus su //
NK019(dza)001:5813: rdzas kyi dbang bcu rdzogs par sbyin //
NK019(dza)001:5815: gnyis pa sgrub pa'i gzhung srong zhing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:5817: rdo rje tshogs te bsnyen pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:5818: nye ba dang ni sgrub pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:5819: sgrub pa chen por sbyar bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:5821: bsnyen sgrub yan lag bzhi la gnyis te /
NK019(dza)001:5825: lta ba chos nyid ji bzhin pa dkyil 'khor rnam gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su rtogs nas /
NK019(dza)001:5826: 'dun pa sems pa'i rnal 'byor la brtan pa thob pas /
NK019(dza)001:5827: rigs chen 'byed pa'i rnal 'byor la zhugs te /
NK019(dza)001:5828: mchog gi dngos grub dbugs chen phyin pa'i rnal 'byor la sbyor ba'i bar chad med lam mo //
NK019(dza)001:5831: rim pa gshoms dang 'brel ba ste /
NK019(dza)001:5833: he ru ka yi sgrub thabs la //
NK019(dza)001:5834: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi gsungs pa las //
NK019(dza)001:5835: rim pa gshoms kyis 'brel ba'i phyir //
NK019(dza)001:5836: bsnyen pa zhes su bshad pa yin //
NK019(dza)001:5839: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi sgor zhugs nas byin dang
NK019(dza)001:5840: ldan pas dngos grub la nye bar byed pa ste
NK019(dza)001:5843: gsang sgor zhugs nas byin ldan phyir //
NK019(dza)001:5844: nye ba'i bsnyen par de brjod do //
NK019(dza)001:5847: tshom bu tshogs kyi sgrub pa dngos la zhugs te /
NK019(dza)001:5848: ma grub na spogs chog dang bcas pas dngos grub
NK019(dza)001:5849: kyi mtshan ma gtan la ma phebs kyi bar de
NK019(dza)001:5850: srid du sgrub par byed pa ste /
NK019(dza)001:5852: rdo rje rigs kyi sgrub pa la //
NK019(dza)001:5853: gang yang bar mtshams mig yeng phyir //
NK019(dza)001:5854: dam pa'i gzhung nyid 'dzin pas na //
NK019(dza)001:5855: sgrub pa zhes byar de brjod do //
NK019(dza)001:5857: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po ni /
NK019(dza)001:5858: rtags dang mtshan ma gtan la phebs nas /
NK019(dza)001:5859: nub tha ma la rang don du dngos grub len
NK019(dza)001:5860: pa'i thabs kyis dbugs chen phyin pa'i rnal 'byor la
NK019(dza)001:5861: sbyar rjes / gzhan don dbang bskur ba'i phrin las la 'jug pa ste /
NK019(dza)001:5863: khrag 'thung las kyi rim pa las //
NK019(dza)001:5865: don mchog mngon du bya ba'i phyir //
NK019(dza)001:5866: sgrub pa chen po zhes su brjod //
NK019(dza)001:5869: ting nge 'dzin la brtan pa ma thob kyang mos
NK019(dza)001:5870: pas spyi'i rnam pa tsam lam du byed pa ste
NK019(dza)001:5872: dang po bsnyen pa la'ang gnyis te /
NK019(dza)001:5874: bsnyen pa'i yan lag dngos so //
NK019(dza)001:5876: rang gzhi lus kun bzang la zhi ba dang /
NK019(dza)001:5877: che mchog la khro dkyil thun thun min gnyis gang
NK019(dza)001:5878: rigs kyi lha lus dkyil du bkod pa'i a nu
NK019(dza)001:5879: rang lugs ltar nyams su len pa'i sgo nas mtshan
NK019(dza)001:5880: dus grangs gsum gang rung gi gzhi'i bsnyen pa kha
NK019(dza)001:5881: skong dang bcas pa byed pa ste /
NK019(dza)001:5883: dus dang grangs dang mtshan ma yin //
NK019(dza)001:5884: bsnyen pa rab tu rdzogs pa gces //
NK019(dza)001:5886: de ltar rtsa bsnyen thems pa'i slob dpon la /
NK019(dza)001:5887: slob bus gsol ba 'debs na snod brtags te /
NK019(dza)001:5888: snod rung du mthong nas bgegs sbyang zhing bsrung ba byas la /
NK019(dza)001:5889: rgyud sbyong ba'i man ngag kyang bstan nas /
NK019(dza)001:5890: slob dpon bdag nyid lha la gnang ba zhu ba'i
NK019(dza)001:5891: don du bsnyen pa kha gso ba la 'jug pa'o
NK019(dza)001:5897: bsham dang brtag bslang sbyang ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:5898: mnan pa byin brlabs bskyed pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:5899: mtshams dang dam sri sgo byang dang //
NK019(dza)001:5900: tshogs bsags gzhal yas khang bskyed pa //
NK019(dza)001:5901: bcu dang gnyis kyis rgyas par 'gyur //
NK019(dza)001:5905: dang po sa yi cho ga ste //
NK019(dza)001:5906: gnyis pa la ni sta gon gnas //
NK019(dza)001:5907: gsum pa 'jug pa'i cho ga bya //
NK019(dza)001:5909: 'dis byin brlabs dang bskyed pa gnyis 'khrugs bsdebs kyis
NK019(dza)001:5910: go barjesa nas nub dang po dang gnyis pa'i bya
NK019(dza)001:5911: ba ston te / de la don bcu gnyis kyi dang po bsham pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:5912: slob dpon bsnyen pa kha gso la bzhugs pa'i bar
NK019(dza)001:5913: slob bus bsag sbyangs dang lhan cig sgrub dbang gi
NK019(dza)001:5914: rdzas sogs 'og tu dgos pa'i yo byad thams cad
NK019(dza)001:5916: gnyis pa sa brtag pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:5918: gnam dang sa dang bar snang rnams //
NK019(dza)001:5919: legs par brtags te las rnams bya //
NK019(dza)001:5920: zhes pas sbyir gnam sa bar snang gi dpyad de gzhi la brtag pa dang /
NK019(dza)001:5921: bye brag 'og tu sa sbyang ba dang 'brel bar brkos te /
NK019(dza)001:5922: sa rang gi mtshan nyid la brtag nas spang blang ma nor bar bya'o //
NK019(dza)001:5924: gnas rab brtag pa'i gal chen yang //
NK019(dza)001:5925: nam mkha' 'khor lo rdo rje dang //
NK019(dza)001:5926: zhes sogs kyis blang bya dang /
NK019(dza)001:5927: skyon gyi gnas dag spang ba ni //
NK019(dza)001:5928: gshin rje gdug pa'i mdung rtse dang //
NK019(dza)001:5929: zhes sogs kyis spang bya bstan no //
NK019(dza)001:5930: gsum pa sa bslang ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:5931: brtags pas rung bar mthong na snang ba mi dang
NK019(dza)001:5932: mi snang ba sa bdag la rin 'jal zhing bden
NK019(dza)001:5935: mngon dang mi mngon bdag po la //
NK019(dza)001:5936: rtsod pa nye bar zhi ba'i phyir //
NK019(dza)001:5937: ser sna spangs pa'i sems kyis ni //
NK019(dza)001:5938: rin dang bden pa brjod la bslang //
NK019(dza)001:5941: sngar ma dul ba'i sa yin na ro lnga bsal
NK019(dza)001:5942: phyir brko ba'i thog mar lto 'phye brtag dgos te
NK019(dza)001:5944: lto 'phye gnas pa'i mtshan nyid ni //
NK019(dza)001:5945: ston zla gsum gyi zla ba la //
NK019(dza)001:5946: nyi ma 'gro ba'i rim pa yis //
NK019(dza)001:5947: mgo shar kha lho g.yon gyis nyal //
NK019(dza)001:5948: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i dgongs pa ltar brtsi ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:5949: nyin gung gi dus su thur shing btsugs pas phyogs btsal nas tshangs zur gyi thig btab ste /
NK019(dza)001:5950: logs bzhi bcad pa'i phyogs rer cha mnyam pa gsum gsum du bgos pa khyim zla bcu gnyis /
NK019(dza)001:5951: de re re bzhin yang sum cu rer gsil ba khyim zhag ste /
NK019(dza)001:5952: lto 'phye gzhogs yon 'og tu bcug nas g.yas skor
NK019(dza)001:5953: gyis zhag re bzhin re'u mig re rer 'pho ba
NK019(dza)001:5954: yin pas na / brko sa gar yod glo bur
NK019(dza)001:5955: du brtag pa'i thig gdab tshul ni 'di lta ste
NK019(dza)001:5956: yin pas na / / sa gzhi gang yin snyoms byas la //
NK019(dza)001:5957: tshangs zur thig gis phyogs btsal nas //
NK019(dza)001:5958: ji tsam 'os pa'i logs bzhi bcad //
NK019(dza)001:5959: de yi steng nas lto 'phye yi //
NK019(dza)001:5960: mgo bo gar gnas zla zhag btsal //
NK019(dza)001:5961: de dang thad drang phyogs gzhan steng //
NK019(dza)001:5962: thig gdab brtsi bya'i tshangs thig ste //
NK019(dza)001:5963: de yi dkyil nas gdengs ka'i bar //
NK019(dza)001:5964: cha mnyam lnga ru bgos byas la //
NK019(dza)001:5965: de yi cha gcig gis tshad pas //
NK019(dza)001:5966: gdengs ka'i rtse nas mar gsum dang //
NK019(dza)001:5967: tshangs thig mdun du phyed dang gnyis //
NK019(dza)001:5968: dor ba'i yas mar cha gcig dang //
NK019(dza)001:5969: phred la cha phyed gnas pa de //
NK019(dza)001:5970: lto ba'i thad yin brko ba'i sa //
NK019(dza)001:5971: mgo bo'i gdengs ka'i gnas lugs ni //
NK019(dza)001:5972: khrums nya ston rar rtsis pa yi //
NK019(dza)001:5973: bu mo'i khyim zla nas brtsams te //
NK019(dza)001:5974: ston gsum shar la dgun gsum lho //
NK019(dza)001:5975: dpyid gsum nub la dbyar gsum byang //
NK019(dza)001:5977: de yang legs grub kyi rgyud chen po las /
NK019(dza)001:5978: nyi ma'i bgrod pa'i tshes gcig la sogs par //
NK019(dza)001:5979: nyin zhag re re bzhin yang cha re re //
NK019(dza)001:5981: nyi ma'i bgrod pa zhes pa khyim zhag dang /
NK019(dza)001:5982: nyin zhag ces pas de dang lto 'byor ba'i nyin
NK019(dza)001:5983: zhag de dang de la brtsi dgos par bstan pas
NK019(dza)001:5984: na / khyim gyi zla zhag 'tshol ba'i man ngag kyang 'di yin te /
NK019(dza)001:5985: gang brtsi'i nyi skar mkha' ros sgyur //
NK019(dza)001:5986: chu tshod bcug la mda' yon zlas //
NK019(dza)001:5987: thob pa lug khyim nas brtsams te //
NK019(dza)001:5988: khyim zla 'das pa'i grangs yin no //
NK019(dza)001:5989: lhag ma mkha' mes sgyur ba la //
NK019(dza)001:5990: chu srang mig gis bgos thob gzhug /
NK019(dza)001:5991: mda' yon zlas thob rtsi bzhin pa'i //
NK019(dza)001:5992: zhag 'di dang bcas da ltar pa'i //
NK019(dza)001:5995: seng ge bu mo srang sdig gzhu //
NK019(dza)001:5996: chu srin bum pa nya rnams ni //
NK019(dza)001:5997: dpyid 'bring nag zla nas bzung ste //
NK019(dza)001:5998: lto 'byor khyim zla bcu gnyis ming //
NK019(dza)001:6000: de ltar brkos nges par byas nas dngos grub rab
NK019(dza)001:6001: 'bring tha gsum gyi ched du sked pa dang lte
NK019(dza)001:6002: ba dang pus mo nub pa tsam du brkos pas
NK019(dza)001:6003: ro lnga'i skyon med na dge zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6004: gal te skyon dang bcas na bsal nas /
NK019(dza)001:6005: de nyid du gter bcug ste stegs bu brtsig pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6006: de ltar yang rtsa rgyud las /
NK019(dza)001:6007: ro lnga'i mtshan ma brtag par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6008: dge bar gyur na der gnas bya //
NK019(dza)001:6009: gal te shis par ma gyur na //
NK019(dza)001:6010: skyes bu thabs la mkhas pa yis //
NK019(dza)001:6011: mnan nam spo ba'i las kyis sbyar //
NK019(dza)001:6012: der ni bsod nams gter ldan zhing //
NK019(dza)001:6013: rin chen lnga la sogs pa'i rdzas //
NK019(dza)001:6014: sa gzhi gter chen rgyas par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6015: bkra shis mchog tu basngagasa pa yin //
NK019(dza)001:6016: sa zhag spos chen rnam lnga'i khu //
NK019(dza)001:6017: bsres pas kun tu gru bzhi ni //
NK019(dza)001:6022: de ltar brkos pas mtshan ma ngan na /
NK019(dza)001:6024: ting 'dzin phyag rgya sngags ldan pas //
NK019(dza)001:6025: mtshan ma'i dngos po kun sbyangs te //
NK019(dza)001:6027: sgyu 'phrul rdo rje las rim las /
NK019(dza)001:6028: kun nas mtshan ma ngan gyur na //
NK019(dza)001:6029: gzhan du bgrod dam zhi ba yi //
NK019(dza)001:6030: me yis rab tu dag par 'gyur //
NK019(dza)001:6031: zhes pas sngags rgya ting nge 'dzin nam sbyin sreg
NK019(dza)001:6032: gis mtshan ma ngan pa rnams zil gyis mnan par
NK019(dza)001:6033: bya ba'o // drug pa bskyed pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6034: sa bzung zhing bsrung ba ste /
NK019(dza)001:6035: gzhi der slob dpon gyis dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bskyed de /
NK019(dza)001:6036: mkha' khyab tu sad pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams mchod /
NK019(dza)001:6037: de nas phyogs bzhi'i slob ma'i gsol gdab dang /
NK019(dza)001:6038: slob dpon gyis kyang nam mkha'i de bzhin gshegs pa bskul nas rang la bsdus te /
NK019(dza)001:6039: zhe sdang rdo rje'i snyems pas bgegs la bka' bsgo zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6040: 'bar ba'i spyan dang rdo rje'i 'gros sogs stangs stabs
NK019(dza)001:6041: kyis kyang bskrad de sa gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin
NK019(dza)001:6042: can du byin gyis brlab pa ni bzung ba'i cho
NK019(dza)001:6043: ga'o // de nas rgyal po btson du bcug na
NK019(dza)001:6044: dmangs cham la phebs pa ltar bgegs rnams ldang mi
NK019(dza)001:6045: ga'o // nus pa'i phyir / rngam glog las /
NK019(dza)001:6046: seng ldeng phur bu sor brgyad pa //
NK019(dza)001:6047: khro bor byin brlabs gdab par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6048: zhes pa ltar khro bcu'i phur gdab kyis bgegs kyi
NK019(dza)001:6049: gtso bo phyogs skyong bcu bcing ba'i sgo nas sa
NK019(dza)001:6051: nub dang po sa'i cho ga'o //
NK019(dza)001:6052: de la dkyil 'khor khang pa rnying pa yin na
NK019(dza)001:6053: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa la'ang sa chog
NK019(dza)001:6055: gnas khang gsar pa yin na ras bris la rten pa'i tshe'ang sa chog byas pa legs te /
NK019(dza)001:6056: sa chog ni sa gzhi la dkyil 'khor bri ba kho na'i ched ma yin gyi /
NK019(dza)001:6057: phyi nang gi bdud dang bar chad gzhom pa'i ched yin pas na /
NK019(dza)001:6058: ras bris kyi phyogs la sa chog mtha' gcig tu
NK019(dza)001:6059: bya mi dgos par 'dod pa la snying po med
NK019(dza)001:6060: do // bdun pa byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6062: yan lag can gyi lhag gnas te /
NK019(dza)001:6064: bsang gtor bya ba'i phyir thog mar las bum dang /
NK019(dza)001:6068: rdul tshon te rdzas lnga brlab pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6069: gnyis pa lha bum slob ma'i sta gon gsum las /
NK019(dza)001:6071: lag len bde phyir nye bsnyen las thig gis bri ba 'dir blangs te /
NK019(dza)001:6073: rdo rje srad bus thig gdab pa'i //
NK019(dza)001:6074: cho ga rnam par bshad bgyi ba //
NK019(dza)001:6075: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar thig gi srad bu'i rgyu
NK019(dza)001:6076: tshad grangs dang thig g.yog sogs nges pas stegs bu
NK019(dza)001:6077: la bdud rtsi lnga'i go ma ye btang la /
NK019(dza)001:6078: gdab thabs dang spyod lam ma 'khrul pas gnam thig
NK019(dza)001:6079: ye shes lnga dang sa thig sku gsung thugs kyi
NK019(dza)001:6080: rang bzhin du cha dbye ba zlum skor dang bcas
NK019(dza)001:6081: pa rtsa dkyil gnyis gang byed kyi lugs ltar btab
NK019(dza)001:6082: pa'i lha gnas so sor dri'i thig le tshom bu
NK019(dza)001:6084: lhar bskyed bstim mchod bstod dang snyan gsan phab ste
NK019(dza)001:6085: sa gzhir bstim pas thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi rang
NK019(dza)001:6086: bzhin du byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6087: de ltar yang he ru ka 'dus pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6088: thig gdab cho ga ji bzhin bya //
NK019(dza)001:6089: dri yi thig le'i mtshan ma dgod //
NK019(dza)001:6090: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor phab cing mchod //
NK019(dza)001:6092: 'di ni rdul tshon du ma zad ras bris kyi phyogs la'ang 'grub na legs te /
NK019(dza)001:6093: snyan gsan dbab pa ni dkyil 'khor bri ba kho
NK019(dza)001:6094: nar ma zad sgrub cing mchod pa'i phyir yang yin
NK019(dza)001:6095: pas so // bum pa sta gon ni /
NK019(dza)001:6096: mtshan nyid dang ldan pa'i bum pa lha grangs dang mnyam pa'am gcig tu bsdus kyang rung ste /
NK019(dza)001:6097: chas su bcug la rdzas so lnga dang dri'i chus bkang ba bkod nas /
NK019(dza)001:6098: rang rang gi lha'am gcig las med na der dkyil
NK019(dza)001:6099: 'khor yongs rdzogs bskyed bstim mchod bstod bzlas pa byas
NK019(dza)001:6103: snod dang ldan pa'i slob ma dag /
NK019(dza)001:6104: mos pas khrus byas sems bskyed de //
NK019(dza)001:6105: lhag par gnas pa ji bzhin bya //
NK019(dza)001:6106: zhes pa ltar sems bskyed cing bgegs dang sdig sgrib
NK019(dza)001:6107: sbyangs pa'i slob bu rnams lhar bskyed de sku gsung
NK019(dza)001:6109: dngos grub kyi ltas brtags pa'i phyir so shing dor ba dang /
NK019(dza)001:6110: rmi lam brtags pa gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6112: rmi lam gsal phyir khyor chu /
NK019(dza)001:6113: bar chad kyis mi sgrib pa'i phyir dpung skud dang phur bu /
NK019(dza)001:6114: mi 'khrug pa'i phyir ku sha'i sngas stan rnams byin nas /
NK019(dza)001:6115: dngos gzhi rmi lam brtags la ngan na nangs par bzlog pa'i cho ga bya ba rnams te /
NK019(dza)001:6117: brgyad pa mtshams bcad pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6119: gsang ba'i las kyi sngon logs su //
NK019(dza)001:6120: bstan pa skyong ba'i mgon po la //
NK019(dza)001:6121: sbyin mchod bsrung ba'i las chen bcol //
NK019(dza)001:6122: zhes pa ltar phyi mtshams rgyal tho dang /
NK019(dza)001:6123: de nas rdo rje nang dag tu //
NK019(dza)001:6124: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar 'bar ba lta ba'i mtshams dang /
NK019(dza)001:6125: khro bo rol pa'i mtshams dang /
NK019(dza)001:6127: sreg byed me'i mtshams rnams kyis nang mtshams bcad do //
NK019(dza)001:6128: dgu pa dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6130: sgrub pa'i rtsal 'di mthar dbyung zhing //
NK019(dza)001:6131: rkyen gyi bar chad bsal ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:6132: gsang ba'i man ngag spyad pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)001:6133: 'jug sred dam sri mnan par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6134: zhes pa ltar bar mtshams dam sri mnan dgos te /
NK019(dza)001:6135: de sngon dam 'dres pas mtshams kyi sbyor ba gzhan gyis mi thub pa'i phyir ro //
NK019(dza)001:6138: de nas las kyi gnas skabs 'dir //
NK019(dza)001:6139: zhes sogs gsungs pa ltar sgo'i phyir las gshin gyi
NK019(dza)001:6140: rten bkod pa la dgug bstim mchod nas bar gcod
NK019(dza)001:6142: bcu gcig pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6143: bsod nams kyi dpung bskyed phyir rgyab rim ci 'grub byed pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6144: bcu gnyis pa gzhal yas khang bskyed pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6146: chos nyid brdal ba'i nam mkha' la //
NK019(dza)001:6147: zhes sogs dbang sgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnas byin gyis brlab cing /
NK019(dza)001:6149: phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'khor dang /
NK019(dza)001:6150: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yo byad brlab pa rnams so //
NK019(dza)001:6151: gnyis pa nye bsnyen la gnyis te /
NK019(dza)001:6156: gnyis pa thig tshon bri ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:6157: gtor ma phyi mtshams rdzas sbyang dang //
NK019(dza)001:6158: bskyed dang rdzas rnams dgod pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:6159: gleng gzhi dbang bskur byin dbab dang //
NK019(dza)001:6160: brda sgo bshags dang dam bca' dang //
NK019(dza)001:6161: byin dbab ma tam dam sri mnan //
NK019(dza)001:6162: rtags gdab mchod pa byin brlab pa //
NK019(dza)001:6163: lnga gnyis bdun gyis rdzogs par 'gyur //
NK019(dza)001:6165: gnyis pa la don bcu bdun las /
NK019(dza)001:6167: thig gis bri ba sngar song bas /
NK019(dza)001:6168: 'dir sta gon gyi lha nam mkhar bteg la /
NK019(dza)001:6170: mtshon pa khrid par byed pa yi //
NK019(dza)001:6171: rdul tshon 'du byas rgyu rnams las //
NK019(dza)001:6172: brnyan ma yi ni dkyil 'khor dag /
NK019(dza)001:6173: so sor brtags te bshad par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6174: zhes pa ltar tshon gyi rgyu grangs sogs nges pas lag pa byin gyis brlabs te /
NK019(dza)001:6175: sngar bsgrubs pa'i tshon gyis lte ba'i phur khung dgang zhing tshon pra brtags nas /
NK019(dza)001:6176: rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor thun thun min gang byed kyi
NK019(dza)001:6177: lugs bzhin du thig ji ltar btab pa'i gzhi la
NK019(dza)001:6181: phyi rol du cha gsum gtor ma btang la /
NK019(dza)001:6185: dkyil 'khor dang sgrub dbang mchod pa'i rdzas rnams kyi bgegs sbyangs shing bsrungs nas /
NK019(dza)001:6186: mtshan ma rnams de dang de'i rnam par bskyed pas byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6187: drug pa rnam pa dgod pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6189: gtso bo gzugs su rdzogs par bri //
NK019(dza)001:6190: 'khor rnams phyag rgya dag tu bya //
NK019(dza)001:6191: phal pa dag la yig 'brus so //
NK019(dza)001:6192: zhes pa'i rim pa ltar lha gnas so sor rang
NK019(dza)001:6193: rang gi mtshan ma bris 'bur gang rigs 'god pa'am
NK019(dza)001:6195: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan dang sgrub dbang gi rdzas rnams so so'i gnas su dgod pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6196: 'khrugs sdebs kyi rim pas bdun pa byin dbab pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6197: zhi khro'i lha tshogs mkha' khyab tu sad pa bdag
NK019(dza)001:6198: gnas dkyil 'khor yo byad dang bcas pa la bstim
NK019(dza)001:6201: dgu pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6202: dbang gi gleng gzhi bshad pas spro ba bskyed nas bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6203: bcu pa brda' sgo dbye ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6204: ye shes bzhi'i sgo phye bas snod bcud dkyil 'khor
NK019(dza)001:6205: gyi rang bzhin du bzhugs pa'i zhal mngon du gyur
NK019(dza)001:6206: pa la / lha dang bdag rig pa'i ngang du gnyis su med par brda phyag bya ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6207: de nas las kyi dbu drang ba dang mtshams gcod sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)001:6210: bcu gsum pa byin dbab pa rnams sgrub thabs ltar byas la /
NK019(dza)001:6211: bcu bzhi pa ma t+aam mnan pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6212: gzugs bcas te dgug bsgral spar la khog pa gzhal yas khang du brlab pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6213: bco lnga pa dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6214: khro bcu'i stangs stabs kyis bgegs dang dam sri gdugs pa can rnams gzir zhing mnan pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6215: bcu drug pa rtags gdab pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6216: bdag nyid ma mo dang mkha' 'gro rnams kyis rang
NK019(dza)001:6217: gi sde tshan du shes pa'i phyir byug rtsi gsum
NK019(dza)001:6219: bcu bdun pa mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ni sgrub thabs ltar ro //
NK019(dza)001:6220: gsum pa sgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK019(dza)001:6225: gsum pa phrin las gzhung bsrang dang //
NK019(dza)001:6226: dzapa tshogs lhag ma mtshams sbrel dang //
NK019(dza)001:6227: sbyin sreg bzod gsol rang stan brlab //
NK019(dza)001:6228: tan gan skabs sbyar nyul le bzlog /
NK019(dza)001:6229: rnam pa bcu yis sgrub gzhung srong //
NK019(dza)001:6232: dang po las gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6234: rdo rje gsang sgo phye nas ni //
NK019(dza)001:6236: rang bzhin yul nas phab nas ni //
NK019(dza)001:6237: sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor der rdzogs bya //
NK019(dza)001:6238: zhes pa ltar rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor thun mong dang
NK019(dza)001:6239: thun mong ma yin pa gang byed kyi zhi khro'i
NK019(dza)001:6240: cho ga gzhung dus drug tu srong ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6242: dzapa khang phye la dam ye 'phro 'du gsum gsal bas dzapa 'bul ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6244: bzhi pa lhag mtshams sbrel ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6245: dzapa khang bsdus rjes tshogs mchod dbul /
NK019(dza)001:6246: gtor ma gsar rnying mtshams sbyar la lhag ma gtong ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6248: rgyas pa'i sreg blugs cho ga bzhin du dbul lo //
NK019(dza)001:6249: drug pa bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6250: skong chen lnga dag gyur dang bcas pa'i cho gas nyams chag bskang zhing bzod par gsol ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6251: bdun pa rang stan brlab pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6252: 'dug pa'i tshe stan byin gyis brlab cing 'gro na phreng bas bsrung du gzhug go //
NK019(dza)001:6255: sgrol ba dang sbyor ba so so'i skabs dang sbyar ste /
NK019(dza)001:6256: gnas su stob pa dang byin gyis brlab pa'i thabs kyis mchod do //
NK019(dza)001:6257: bcu pa nyul le bzlog pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6258: thun mthar dus drug gi nyul le brtags la rang rang gi gnyen pos bzlog par bya zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6259: dus der dngos grub ster ba'i pho nya re yang
NK019(dza)001:6260: 'ong bas nyul le bzlog pa'i rjes de ma thag
NK019(dza)001:6261: par byin dbab pa'ang bya ba yin no //
NK019(dza)001:6262: bzhi pa sgrub pa chen po la gnyis te /
NK019(dza)001:6267: bzhi pa rtags bsham sbyin sreg dang //
NK019(dza)001:6268: dngos grub blang dang dbang bskur dang //
NK019(dza)001:6269: bkra shis smon lam gtor ma gter //
NK019(dza)001:6270: bsdu dang gnas bsrung lnga gnyis gcig /
NK019(dza)001:6272: gnyis pa la bcu gcig las /
NK019(dza)001:6275: de ltar bsgrubs pas grub pa'i rtags mtshan gtan la phebs pa dang /
NK019(dza)001:6276: nub tha ma la dngos grub kyi rdzas bsham zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6278: dbang gi sregs blugs phul nas /
NK019(dza)001:6280: rmad byung sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK019(dza)001:6281: 'jug dang dngos grub gsol ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:6282: dbang bskur ba yi las rnams bya //
NK019(dza)001:6284: bzhi pa dngos grub blang zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6285: lnga pa dbang bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6286: sgrub pa po bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs te
NK019(dza)001:6287: tshom bu'i 'khor dang bcas pas rang don du dngos
NK019(dza)001:6288: grub blangs rjes / gzhan don slob bu rnams rtsa rgyud kyi rnal 'byor 'jug pa'i le'u'am /
NK019(dza)001:6289: dgongs 'dus kyi dus dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa gang rung gi cho gas dkyil 'khor du bcug nas /
NK019(dza)001:6290: rtsa rgyud kyi rdo rje dbang gi le'u las bshad
NK019(dza)001:6291: pa ltar rgyud lugs kyi dbang chu bo bzhis bsdus
NK019(dza)001:6292: pa'i sum cu rtsa drug snod kyi theg tshad dang
NK019(dza)001:6294: de nas rjes cho ga gi rim pa /
NK019(dza)001:6300: gnas su bkra shis la sogs kyis //
NK019(dza)001:6301: sgrub pa rdzogs par mthar dbyung ngo //
NK019(dza)001:6303: dbang dang dngos grub brtan pa'i phyir shis pa brjod cing /
NK019(dza)001:6304: las byas pa don yod par bya ba'i phyir mar me smon lam gdab /
NK019(dza)001:6306: gtor ma la sogs rdzas rnams ni //
NK019(dza)001:6307: cha gsum dag tu bgos nas kyang //
NK019(dza)001:6308: gcig ni sbyin sreg las chog bya //
NK019(dza)001:6309: gcig ni rnal 'byor longs spyod gter //
NK019(dza)001:6311: zhes pas ltar gtor ma cha gsum du bgos la /
NK019(dza)001:6312: zhi ba'i sreg blugs dang gter du sba /
NK019(dza)001:6313: cha gcig gis gtor skyong bya zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6314: lhag chog dang brtan ma'ang bskyang ngo //
NK019(dza)001:6316: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor 'od gsal du bsdu zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6317: de las langs nas mtshams bkrol te /
NK019(dza)001:6318: mtshan ma'i dkyil 'khor bsdus la rdul tshon chu bor gshegs so //
NK019(dza)001:6319: bcu gcig pa gnas bsrung ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6320: sgrub pa po rnams zhag gcig gi ring phyi rol du mi 'gro zhing mtshams rim gyis dgrol lo //
NK019(dza)001:6321: gnyis pa man ngag gi lugs mdo yongs rdzogs kyi
NK019(dza)001:6322: dkyil 'khor du theg pa thams cad 'dus pa'i mdo
NK019(dza)001:6323: dbang rtsa ba so drug las yan lag rags pa
NK019(dza)001:6324: brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye nas bskur tshul ni
NK019(dza)001:6325: / slob dpon chen po bde ba gsal mdzad kyi
NK019(dza)001:6326: las tho'i dgongs pa yin pas man ngag gi lugs
NK019(dza)001:6327: / zhes bya ste / smin mos kyi khyad par ni /
NK019(dza)001:6328: 'dir nye bsnyen dang sgrub pa gnyis la zhag bdun
NK019(dza)001:6329: re'i zhal gsal yod pas mos slob gtso che zhing
NK019(dza)001:6330: / de gnyis zhag grangs 'dra bar mdzad pa sgyu 'phrul lam rim las /
NK019(dza)001:6331: zla phyed phyed zhal nye bsnyen pa //
NK019(dza)001:6333: bco lnga mar phyed sgrub pa ste //
NK019(dza)001:6335: zhes pa'i lugs dang 'dra bar snang yang /
NK019(dza)001:6336: 'dir nye bsnyen dang sgrub pa gnyis rgyud lung gi
NK019(dza)001:6337: dkyil 'khor so so ba yin pas khyad par che'o
NK019(dza)001:6338: // de ltar nges par byas nas /
NK019(dza)001:6339: ji ltar bskur tshul la gnyis te /
NK019(dza)001:6340: phun sum tshogs pa lngas gzhi bzung ba /
NK019(dza)001:6341: bsnyen sgrub bzhis gzhung srong dang 'brel bar chu bo bzhi'i dbang bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6344: dang po phun sum tshogs ldan te //
NK019(dza)001:6345: tshad phyin rab 'byams slob dpon gyis //
NK019(dza)001:6346: snod dang ldan pa'i 'khor bsdus nas //
NK019(dza)001:6347: gzhung dang mthun pa'i gnas dag tu //
NK019(dza)001:6348: sa chog rdzogs byas gnas khang ldan //
NK019(dza)001:6349: dgos pa tshang ba'i yo byad rdzogs //
NK019(dza)001:6350: dus cha bzhi yi dang po la //
NK019(dza)001:6351: nyi zla gza' skar tshes grangs brtag /
NK019(dza)001:6353: de dag gi don ni sngar bshad zin to //
NK019(dza)001:6355: slob dpon gzhi'i bsnyen pa sngon du thems pas slob ma bzung zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6356: rang gi bsnyen pa kha gsos rjes bsnyen sgrub la 'jug pa yin pas /
NK019(dza)001:6358: bsnyen pa'i yan lag phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo /
NK019(dza)001:6359: nye bsnyen gyi yan lag nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo /
NK019(dza)001:6360: sgrub pa'i yan lag sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo /
NK019(dza)001:6361: sgrub chen gyi yan lag gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo bskur ba'i rim pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6363: gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK019(dza)001:6364: gang bskur bya'i dbang gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6367: yo ga la sogs theg drug la //
NK019(dza)001:6368: phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bos bya //
NK019(dza)001:6370: lha mi nas yo ga'i bar bya spyod gcig tu
NK019(dza)001:6371: byas pa'i dkyil 'khor drug tu snang ba rigs bsdus
NK019(dza)001:6375: dang po phyi dbang rgyud chu bo //
NK019(dza)001:6376: mtshan nyid sde gsum lugs dag tu //
NK019(dza)001:6377: nye'u 'don srog skyob sbyin pa bkye //
NK019(dza)001:6378: nad gso'i sman dang klog gdon bya //
NK019(dza)001:6379: rgyud dgrol chos dang lam 'phrang bsal //
NK019(dza)001:6381: las dang po la phyang tshul bstan //
NK019(dza)001:6386: thog mar dkyil 'khor khang pa gsar rnying gi khyad
NK019(dza)001:6387: kyis 'dor len shes pas dkyil chog ltar sa'i cho
NK019(dza)001:6388: ga bya zhing / sa sbyang ba'i tshe stegs bu
NK019(dza)001:6389: la ba byung dang spos lngas chag chag 'debs pa
NK019(dza)001:6390: las 'dir bdud rtsi lnga mi bsre ba khyad par
NK019(dza)001:6391: ga bya zhing / ro // spos lnga'i ngos 'dzin kyang gzhan dang mi 'dra ste /
NK019(dza)001:6393: ga bur tsan+dana li shi dang //
NK019(dza)001:6394: rgya spos dz+aa ti pha la lnga //
NK019(dza)001:6396: de nas dge ba'i dpung bskyed pa'i phyir /
NK019(dza)001:6398: srog bslu bya zhing ri rgya klungs rgya bsdam pa /
NK019(dza)001:6401: lam 'phrang bsal ba sogs rgyab rim ci 'grub sngon du gtong zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6402: khyad par gnas de nyid du slob ma 'dus pa rnams kyis /
NK019(dza)001:6403: 'bum lnga dang dpang skongs kyi gsung rab klog /
NK019(dza)001:6404: mched kyi mi grangs sam lo grangs kyi s+aats+tsha gdab /
NK019(dza)001:6405: khyad par sbyin pa'i nang tshan phyi nang gi thugs dam skong ba'i phyir du /
NK019(dza)001:6406: phyi ltar cha gsum gyi dkyil 'khor bshams nas mgron rnam bzhi la spyir mchod sbyin bya zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6407: khyad par sgos kyi mchod gtor kyang ci nus gtong /
NK019(dza)001:6408: nang ltar na ma mo'i rgyud las /
NK019(dza)001:6409: cho ga 'di la brten byed na //
NK019(dza)001:6410: cha mthun sprul pa'i ma mo mnyes //
NK019(dza)001:6411: 'jig rten dbang chen thams cad kyis //
NK019(dza)001:6412: byang chub sems ltar bkur sti byed //
NK019(dza)001:6413: tshe dang dbang thang 'phel ba dang //
NK019(dza)001:6414: bsgo ba'i tshig rnams nyan par 'gyur //
NK019(dza)001:6416: lha bu dri med 'chi ba 'di yis slus //
NK019(dza)001:6417: mi la sogs pa gzhan la smos ci dgos //
NK019(dza)001:6419: 'di yi yon tan bsod nams kyis //
NK019(dza)001:6420: phyi ma'i dngos grub mchog ster te //
NK019(dza)001:6421: bsod nams mchog ni bla na med //
NK019(dza)001:6422: mtho ris thar pa'i lam thob ste //
NK019(dza)001:6423: rig 'dzin sa la skyel bar byed //
NK019(dza)001:6424: 'di yi bsod nams gong nyid du //
NK019(dza)001:6425: cho ga gzhan gyis rnyogs pa med //
NK019(dza)001:6426: dam la gnas pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK019(dza)001:6427: cho ga 'di la brten byas na //
NK019(dza)001:6428: ji ltar bsam pa bzhin du 'grub //
NK019(dza)001:6429: ma dang mkha' 'gros byin gyis brlab //
NK019(dza)001:6430: sangs rgyas rnams kyis dngos grub ster //
NK019(dza)001:6431: zhes mthar thug gi phan yon kyang mtha' yas pa'i phyir //
NK019(dza)001:6432: ma mo gling bzhi'i mdos kyis phyi cha mthun sprul pa'i ma mo bskang zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6434: phyi rabs rnal 'byor dam ldan la //
NK019(dza)001:6435: ma mo khros shing log gyur par //
NK019(dza)001:6436: srid pa spyi mdos mi 'grub na //
NK019(dza)001:6437: gling gi bskang ba ngas bshad do //
NK019(dza)001:6438: zhes slob dpon chen po pad+mas ma mo rin chen
NK019(dza)001:6439: phra bkod las phyung ba gling gi bskang ba lta
NK019(dza)001:6440: bu zhig gis mchod pas don 'grub bo //
NK019(dza)001:6441: de bzhin du nang gsang rang bzhin gyi ma mo ste bzhi po bskang zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6442: khyad par tshogs las kyis nyams chag skong ba rnams bya'o //
NK019(dza)001:6443: de nas mched gsar rnying gi khyad par gyis bsre bsnan byas te /
NK019(dza)001:6444: gab pa'i dbang le drug gi dang po spyi dbang
NK019(dza)001:6445: chen po'i gleng gzhi'i le'u las gsungs pa phyag rdor
NK019(dza)001:6446: ngan song gnas 'dren gyi dkyil 'khor du rgyud dgrol
NK019(dza)001:6447: ba'i zab mo'i chos dang gleng gzhi bshad pas nges
NK019(dza)001:6448: shes bskyed nas / rgyud sbyong zhing snod rung du
NK019(dza)001:6449: sgrub pa'i phyir mchog dbang bcu drug sgo 'byed kyi
NK019(dza)001:6450: tshul du bskur te nub dang po'i bya ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6451: de nas nub gnyis pa nas bzung phyi dbang rnams zhag grangs rgyas bsdus skabs dang sbyar te /
NK019(dza)001:6455: byang sems bzhi'i dkyil 'khor bsham zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6456: so so'i sgrub mchod gtor cho ga dang bcas song ba dang /
NK019(dza)001:6457: las dang po pa rnams rang rang gi nges 'byung ste /
NK019(dza)001:6460: byang sems kyis mtha' gnyis las nges par 'byung ba'i
NK019(dza)001:6461: tshul bzhis so so'i sdom pa 'bogs chog gis dkyil
NK019(dza)001:6465: de nas phyi rgyud theg pa yis //
NK019(dza)001:6466: rigs gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig dang //
NK019(dza)001:6467: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bzhengs //
NK019(dza)001:6468: spyan drangs mchod pa sbyin sreg snyeg /
NK019(dza)001:6469: bzlas brjod bsnyen sgrub rdzogs pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:6471: kri yo ga gnyis rang rang gi sta gon sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)001:6472: kri ya rtsa ba'i lha rigs gsum nyi shu rtsa gcig gi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK019(dza)001:6473: yo ga rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor so so'i lugs bzhin bzhengs nas /
NK019(dza)001:6475: ye shes pa spyan drangs la mchod bstod bzlas pa dang /
NK019(dza)001:6476: 'grub na sbyin sreg kyang dbul zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6477: de ltar sgrub mchod grub pa dang bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs rjes /
NK019(dza)001:6478: slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i cho ga rnams bya ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6479: gnyis pa gang bskur bya'i dbang ni /
NK019(dza)001:6481: phyi dbang rtsa ba bcu po la //
NK019(dza)001:6482: yan lag brgya rtsa brgyad du bskur //
NK019(dza)001:6483: rgyud kyi chu bo'i las tho'o //
NK019(dza)001:6485: de la phyi dbang rtsa ba bcu ni /
NK019(dza)001:6486: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6487: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6488: gnyis pa rtags kyi mtshan ma'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6489: gsum pa thugs rje gzungs kyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6490: bzhi pa shes rab bum pa'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6491: lnga pa khyad par gdan gyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6492: drug pa rgyal srid rin chen dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6493: bdun pa bkra shis rdzas kyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6494: brgyad pa shes bya ma rmongs dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6495: dgu pa mdzes pa rgyan cha'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6496: bcu pa dbang sgyur ming gi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6499: de las yan lag rags pa brgya rtsa brgyad du dbye ba la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6501: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6502: chu bo bzhi yi dbang gi rim pa las //
NK019(dza)001:6503: dang po rgyud kyi chu bo rnam grangs bcu //
NK019(dza)001:6504: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags nyi shu dang //
NK019(dza)001:6505: gnyis pa mtshan ma rtags dbang nyi shu drug /
NK019(dza)001:6506: gsum pa thugs rje gzungs kyi dbang bcu gcig /
NK019(dza)001:6507: bzhi pa shes rab bum pa'i dbang la gcig /
NK019(dza)001:6508: lnga pa khyad par gdan gyi dbang la gsum //
NK019(dza)001:6509: drug pa rgyal srid rin chen dbang bcu drug /
NK019(dza)001:6510: bdun pa bkra shis dbang la'ang bcu drug go //
NK019(dza)001:6511: brgyad pa shes bya ma rmongs dbang la bdun //
NK019(dza)001:6512: dgu pa mdzes pa rgyan cha'i dbang la drug /
NK019(dza)001:6513: bcu pa dbang bsgyur ming gi dbang la gnyis //
NK019(dza)001:6517: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags nyi shu ni //
NK019(dza)001:6518: cod pan lha mo seng ge glang po che //
NK019(dza)001:6519: ras gos khrus bum ming 'dogs rgyan bye brag /
NK019(dza)001:6520: yi ge mda' gzhu btsun mo shing rta'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6521: chibs mchog shan gri gseg par na bza' ngur //
NK019(dza)001:6522: 'bras chan r+ts+wa stan sbrang rtsi bur sbrang ste //
NK019(dza)001:6523: rgya che rol pa'i 'gro 'dul mtshan nyid dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6524: gnyis pa mtshan ma rtags dbang nyer drug ni //
NK019(dza)001:6525: ri rab mchod rten dpag bsam shing rgya mtsho //
NK019(dza)001:6526: sa gzhi bdud rtsi dar bu khri rkang dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6527: me tog rnga yab rdul yab sbrang yab dang //
NK019(dza)001:6528: bla re rgyal mtshan gdugs dang nya rgya dang //
NK019(dza)001:6529: ska rags spos lnga snying po rin chen lnga //
NK019(dza)001:6530: 'bru lnga stag tsher seng tsher shu dag dang //
NK019(dza)001:6531: dbang lag kan+da ka ste kri ya'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6532: phyag na rdo rje dbang bskur rgyud las bkrol //
NK019(dza)001:6533: gsum pa thugs rje gzungs dbang bcu gcig la //
NK019(dza)001:6534: sku gzugs phyag rgya gsung gzungs yig 'bru dang //
NK019(dza)001:6535: thugs kyi gser thur me long 'khor lo dung //
NK019(dza)001:6536: yon tan me tog phreng ba phrin las la //
NK019(dza)001:6537: rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram mo //
NK019(dza)001:6538: bzhi pa shes rab bum pa gcig pu nyid //
NK019(dza)001:6539: lnga pa khyad par gdan dbang zil gnon gyi //
NK019(dza)001:6540: seng ge mun sel nyi ma tsha sel zla //
NK019(dza)001:6541: drug pa rgyal srid rin chen bcu drug ni //
NK019(dza)001:6542: 'khor lo rta mchog glang po nor bu dang //
NK019(dza)001:6543: blon po btsun mo dmag dpon rin chen bdun //
NK019(dza)001:6544: ral gri mda' gzhu gnam ral shan gri dang //
NK019(dza)001:6545: zhwa dang khab skud na bza' phyags mchog dang //
NK019(dza)001:6546: krish+na'i pags gdan nye ba'i rat+na dgu //
NK019(dza)001:6547: bdun pa bkra shis rdzas dbang bcu drug ni //
NK019(dza)001:6548: yungs kar zho phor rtsa dur li khri mtshal //
NK019(dza)001:6549: me long 'bud dung gi'u wam bilba rdzas //
NK019(dza)001:6550: dpal be'u 'khor lo pad+ma rgyal mtshan dang //
NK019(dza)001:6551: bum pa gdugs dung gser nya rtags bkra shis //
NK019(dza)001:6552: brgyad pa shes bya ma rmongs dbang bdun ni //
NK019(dza)001:6553: rgya gram cod pan p+au dza ka p+aa li //
NK019(dza)001:6554: phyag shing 'chad pod rdo rje dril bu'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6555: dgu pa mdzes pa rgyan chas dbang drug ni //
NK019(dza)001:6556: dbu rgyan dpung rgyan zhabs gdub phyag gdub dang //
NK019(dza)001:6557: do shal dar gyi cod pan dbang bskur ro //
NK019(dza)001:6558: bcu pa rgyu dang 'bras bu'i ming dbang ste //
NK019(dza)001:6559: dkon mchog slob dpon pha rol phyin las gras //
NK019(dza)001:6560: 'jig rten tha mal zhen ldog rgyu yi ming //
NK019(dza)001:6561: rdo rje dbang phyug ces pa 'bras bu'i ming //
NK019(dza)001:6562: de ltar phyi dbang rgyud kyi chu bo la //
NK019(dza)001:6563: dbang don rgyas pa yan lag brgya rtsa brgyad //
NK019(dza)001:6565: dang po rgyal po bka' rtags nyi shu'i dbang ni /
NK019(dza)001:6566: mtshan nyid theg pa'i dbang ste /
NK019(dza)001:6569: rang rgyal gsum la de'i nang nas btus te dbang bskur dgos pas /
NK019(dza)001:6570: lha mi'i theg pa'i dbang la /
NK019(dza)001:6571: cod pan nas btsun mo'i bar bcu gcig dang /
NK019(dza)001:6572: de'i steng du lhag por rgya bod kyi yi ge rnams bskur /
NK019(dza)001:6573: nyan thos kyi theg pa'i dbang la /
NK019(dza)001:6575: bdun pa ming dbang gi steng du /
NK019(dza)001:6576: shing rta nas sbrang rtsi'i bar brgyad dang /
NK019(dza)001:6577: lhag por mu ne'i gzungs rnams bskur /
NK019(dza)001:6578: rang rgyal gyi theg pa'i dbang la /
NK019(dza)001:6584: sbrang rtsi ste drug gi steng du lhag por rten 'brel bcu gnyis kyi gzugs rnams bskur /
NK019(dza)001:6585: byang sems kyi theg pa la rgyal po bka' rtags kyi dbang nyi shu po tshang bar bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6586: de nas kri ya'i dkyil 'khor du gnyis pa mtshan ma rtags dbang nyer drug dang /
NK019(dza)001:6587: yo ga'i dkyil 'khor du gsum pa thugs rje gzungs dbang bcu gcig nas /
NK019(dza)001:6588: bcu pa rgyu dang 'bras bu'i ming dbang gi bar te drug cu re gnyis bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6589: de ltar phyi dbang brgya rtsa brgyad kyi steng du /
NK019(dza)001:6590: lha mi nyan rang gsum de'i nang nas btus shing
NK019(dza)001:6591: rang rang gi sgos chos lhag po dang bcas sum
NK019(dza)001:6592: cu so gcig byung ba rnams bsnan pas phyi dbang
NK019(dza)001:6593: la chig brgya so dgur 'gyur zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6594: de thams cad rdzas dbang rkyang pa'i grangs yin pas /
NK019(dza)001:6595: da dung de'i steng du so so'i lha dbang bskur dgos la /
NK019(dza)001:6596: de yang phyi dbang gi skabs 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi
NK019(dza)001:6597: lha grangs dbye bsdu'i khyad par las grangs mtha' gcig
NK019(dza)001:6598: tu bzhag dka' bar snang ngo //
NK019(dza)001:6599: gnyis pa nye bsnyen gyi yan lag nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo bskur ba la /
NK019(dza)001:6600: gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK019(dza)001:6601: gang bskur bya'i dbang gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6604: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga la //
NK019(dza)001:6605: nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bos bya //
NK019(dza)001:6607: nang dbang gang du bskur ba ma h+aa yo ga'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK019(dza)001:6608: tshogs chen 'dus pa thun mong pa'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK019(dza)001:6609: 'dren pa'i las byang che ler gsungs pa nyid yin pas /
NK019(dza)001:6610: de bshad pa la gsum ste /
NK019(dza)001:6616: de nas nang dbang chu bo'i dus //
NK019(dza)001:6617: dpang skongs sbyin sreg sta gon bya //
NK019(dza)001:6618: zhes pas dpang bskongs klog cing /
NK019(dza)001:6619: zhi gzhung bsrang nas tshogs dang zhi ba'i sbyin sreg dbul ba sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)001:6620: yan lag rab gnas rdzas lnga brlab pa dang /
NK019(dza)001:6621: yan lag can lha bum slob ma'i sta gon rnams bya ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:6629: cha gsum gser skyems gsar pa 'gyed //
NK019(dza)001:6630: rgyal chen phyogs skyong bka' bsgos la //
NK019(dza)001:6631: phyi mtshams bsrung ba'i phrin las bcol //
NK019(dza)001:6632: bar mtshams khro bcus mtshams bcad de //
NK019(dza)001:6633: 'jug sred mnan la nang mtshams bcad //
NK019(dza)001:6634: ces pas nangs par cha gsum gyi gtor ma dang gser skyems btang /
NK019(dza)001:6635: drag sngags thun brab spos rol dang bcas pa'i tsham rngams kyis bgegs bskrad de /
NK019(dza)001:6636: sgrub khang nas gom pa bdun cu gzhal ba'i sar
NK019(dza)001:6637: rgyal chen bzhi dang phyogs skyong bcu'i tho bsdams pas
NK019(dza)001:6638: phyi mtsham bcad / khro bcu'i phur bu sngar sa
NK019(dza)001:6639: chog dus btab na 'dir phrin las bskul ba tsam
NK019(dza)001:6640: dang ma btab na 'dir gdab cing /
NK019(dza)001:6641: dam sri mnan pas bar mtshams bcad /
NK019(dza)001:6645: sreg byed me ste bzhis nang mtshams gcod cing /
NK019(dza)001:6646: gcad bya gcod byed thams cad dmigs med du rgyas
NK019(dza)001:6647: 'debs pas gsang ba de kho na nyid kyi mtshams
NK019(dza)001:6648: kyang bcad do // gnyis pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6650: dbang sgyur phyag rgya tshogs chen rdzogs //
NK019(dza)001:6651: gnas 'khor yo byad byin brlabs nas //
NK019(dza)001:6653: dbang sgyur gyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnas /
NK019(dza)001:6654: phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis 'khor /
NK019(dza)001:6655: tshogs chen 'dus pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yo byad brlabs pa rnams so //
NK019(dza)001:6658: go ma ye btang gzungs ma brlab //
NK019(dza)001:6659: thig tshon phyag rgya rdzas chen dgod //
NK019(dza)001:6661: zhes pa sta gon gyi lha btegs nas /
NK019(dza)001:6662: stegs bu la dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga'i go ma ye btang la /
NK019(dza)001:6663: rang nyid lhar gsal bas gzungs ma yum du brlabs
NK019(dza)001:6664: pa'i gnyis ka'i gnas lngar rigs lnga dang mkha' gsang
NK019(dza)001:6666: gnam thig dang sa thig gi bya ba sngar lha sta gon gyi sngon du btab zin pas /
NK019(dza)001:6667: 'dir lag pa byin gyis brlabs nas sngar bsgrubs pa'i
NK019(dza)001:6668: rdul tshon thig ji ltar btab pa'i gzhi la rim
NK019(dza)001:6669: par dgye bas / tshogs chen 'dus pas thun mong ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK019(dza)001:6670: khyams rim dgu pa'i lte ba rtsibs brgyad pa'i khro dkyil gyi steng du zhi dkyil bkod de /
NK019(dza)001:6671: zhi khro brtsegs ma'i lugs su bzhengs la /
NK019(dza)001:6673: mchod rdzas sgrub dbang gi rdzas sogs yo byad thams cad tshang bar dgod cing byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6676: zhi khro'i lam rim gzhung bsrangs bskyed //
NK019(dza)001:6677: spyan drangs mchod bstod sbyin sreg dbul //
NK019(dza)001:6678: bzlas pas bsnyen sgrub tshogs mchod bya //
NK019(dza)001:6679: zhag bdun dus drug rdzogs pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:6680: zhes pas dus drug tu zhi khro'i rten dang brten
NK019(dza)001:6681: par bcas pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom
NK019(dza)001:6682: zhing / rang bzhin ye shes kyi 'khor lo spyan drangs nas gnyis su med par byas pa la /
NK019(dza)001:6683: mchod bstod sogs las kyi gzhung bsrangs nas /
NK019(dza)001:6684: dzapa khang phye ste gsal ba gsum dang ldan pas bzlas bsnyen bya zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6685: sbyin sreg dang tshogs gtor rnams kyang gtong ste dkyil 'khor sgrub mchod do //
NK019(dza)001:6688: kun byas dbang phyug rig pas 'jug /
NK019(dza)001:6689: bu rnams phrin gdags sems bskyed de //
NK019(dza)001:6691: zhes pas slob dpon gyis sgrub mchod kyi bya ba kun byas nas /
NK019(dza)001:6692: zhag bdun rdzogs pa'i tha ma la bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du rig pas zhugs rjes /
NK019(dza)001:6693: slob bu rnams kun rdzob dang don dam pa'i byang
NK019(dza)001:6694: chub tu sems bskyed de dkyil 'khor du phyi dang
NK019(dza)001:6695: nang gi 'jug pa rim bzhin bya'o //
NK019(dza)001:6696: gnyis pa gang bskur bya'i dbang ni /
NK019(dza)001:6698: de la nang dbang bcu gcig po //
NK019(dza)001:6699: yan lag drug brgya drug gis bskur //
NK019(dza)001:6702: de la nang dbang rtsa ba bcu gcig ni /
NK019(dza)001:6703: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6704: de nas nang du 'jug par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6705: dang po gsang ba nyan pa'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6706: gnyis pa rnam bzhi las kyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6707: gsum pa rgyal theb 'chad pa'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6708: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal po'i dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6709: lnga pa zil gnon gdan gyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6710: drug pa khyad par rin chen dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6711: bdun pa phyag rgya gzugs brnyan dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6712: brgyad pa ye shes thugs kyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6713: dgu pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6714: bcu pa bdud 'dul bkra shis dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6715: bcu gcig gsang ba ming gi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6717: de las yan lag drug brgya drug tu dbye ba la bstan bshad gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6719: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6720: gnyis pa 'byung ba'i chu bo bcu gcig la //
NK019(dza)001:6721: dang po gnyis gsum bzhi lnga re re la //
NK019(dza)001:6722: drug bdun bdun la lnga brgya brgyad cu gsum //
NK019(dza)001:6723: brgyad dgu re re bcu pa bkra shis brgyad //
NK019(dza)001:6724: bcu gcig gsang ba ming gi dbang de gcig /
NK019(dza)001:6728: dang po gsang ba nyan dbang rna ba la //
NK019(dza)001:6729: rat+na rigs kyis bskur dang bsgrags rdzas byin //
NK019(dza)001:6730: gnyis pa rnam bzhi las dbang lag pa la //
NK019(dza)001:6731: las kyi rigs kyis bskur dang bsgrags rdzas byin //
NK019(dza)001:6732: gsum pa rgyal theb 'chad dbang lce la ste //
NK019(dza)001:6733: pad+ma rigs kyis bskur dang bsgrags rdzas byin //
NK019(dza)001:6734: bzhi pa rdo rje rgyal dbang spyi bo la //
NK019(dza)001:6735: de bzhin rigs kyis dbang bskur bsgrags rdzas byin //
NK019(dza)001:6736: lnga pa zil gnon gdan dbang rkang pa la //
NK019(dza)001:6737: 'jig rten dregs pa khyo shugs gdan dbang bskur //
NK019(dza)001:6738: drug pa thun mong ma yin rat+na bdun //
NK019(dza)001:6739: 'khor los dbang bskur skye ba bzhir dbang sgyur //
NK019(dza)001:6740: btsun mo 'byung ba bzhi yis mnyes pa 'bul //
NK019(dza)001:6741: dmag dpon tshul dgus pha rol dmag dpung 'joms //
NK019(dza)001:6742: khyim bdag tshad med bzhi yis chab srid 'dzin //
NK019(dza)001:6743: glang chen stobs bcus bdag dang gzhan don mdzad //
NK019(dza)001:6744: rta mchog rdzu 'phrul myur mgyogs gnas slebs byed //
NK019(dza)001:6745: nor bu rin chen rnam bzhi re 'dod skong //
NK019(dza)001:6746: bdun pa phyag rgya gzugs brnyan dbang bskur ba //
NK019(dza)001:6747: dkyil 'khor dgu brtsegs dpal gyi phyag rgya'i rim //
NK019(dza)001:6748: kun gyi spyi dpal kun bzang bde chen dkyil //
NK019(dza)001:6749: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor dang //
NK019(dza)001:6750: che mchog yab yum chos sku rdzogs pa'i dkyil //
NK019(dza)001:6751: khrag 'thung 'bar ba rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK019(dza)001:6752: d+aa ki las kyi dkyil 'khor sum cu gnyis //
NK019(dza)001:6753: skyes bu king chen bco brgyad sgrol ba'i dkyil //
NK019(dza)001:6754: khrag 'thung rol dkyil sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor dang //
NK019(dza)001:6755: mgyogs 'gro yid kyis dkyil 'khor phyogs pho nya //
NK019(dza)001:6756: dam tshig chen po ma sring 'og pho nya //
NK019(dza)001:6757: rdo rje 'chang gi dkyil 'khor slob dpon dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6758: bde chen gcig dang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK019(dza)001:6759: che mchog gnyis dang bdun cu rtsa brgyad dang //
NK019(dza)001:6760: drug bcu bzhi bcu so gnyis bco brgyad bdun //
NK019(dza)001:6761: bzhi dang sum brgya dkyil 'khor brgyad lha'i grangs //
NK019(dza)001:6762: dkyil 'khor tha ma byin brlabs slob dpon dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6763: dkyil 'khor dgu yi rim par slob dpon gdan //
NK019(dza)001:6764: ma gtogs lha la lnga brgya brgyad cu gsum //
NK019(dza)001:6765: brgyad pa ye shes thugs dbang gnas lngar bskur //
NK019(dza)001:6766: ye shes lnga'am dgu rtags me mar byin //
NK019(dza)001:6767: dgu pa sku gsung thugs kyi dbang bskur ba //
NK019(dza)001:6768: spyi bo lce snying lte ba gsang gnas su //
NK019(dza)001:6769: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las lnga re re //
NK019(dza)001:6770: phyag rgya sngags dang ting 'dzin ldan pas bskur //
NK019(dza)001:6771: bcu pa bdud 'dul bkra shis rdzas brgyad lus //
NK019(dza)001:6772: bcu gcig gsang ba ming dbang rna snying la //
NK019(dza)001:6773: rdo rje rtsal gyi thig le sbyin par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6774: des na nang dbang 'byung ba'i chu bo la //
NK019(dza)001:6775: drug brgya drug tu gyes pa bskur bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:6777: 'dir bdun pa phyag rgya gzugs brnyan gyi skabs su /
NK019(dza)001:6778: bde chen gcig dang bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK019(dza)001:6781: bde chen gcig dang brgyad cu rtsa gnyis dang //
NK019(dza)001:6783: zur ham gyi phyag len rgyun bzhin bris pa'i tsaklira
NK019(dza)001:6784: yang zhi ba zhe gnyis kyi steng du rigs chung
NK019(dza)001:6785: gi sems dpa' yab yum bzhi bcu bsnan te /
NK019(dza)001:6786: zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha
NK019(dza)001:6787: grangs la brgyad cu rtsa gnyis su mdzad pa ni
NK019(dza)001:6788: mi rigs te / 'dren pa'i las byang che ler /
NK019(dza)001:6789: de nas bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang pos
NK019(dza)001:6790: skad cig yud la nam mkha' gang nas gang du
NK019(dza)001:6791: khyab pa thams cad du dbang gi dkyil 'khor zhi
NK019(dza)001:6792: khro'i lha lnga brgya dang brgyad cu rtsa gsum gyis
NK019(dza)001:6794: zhes spyi bsdoms kyi grangs bshad nas /
NK019(dza)001:6796: bang rim dang po'i steng du zhi ba'i lha zhe gnyis dgod /
NK019(dza)001:6797: ces zhi ba rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor gyi lha grangs zhe gnyis su gsungs pa dang /
NK019(dza)001:6798: phyogs mtshams steng 'og dang man+dala gyi rtsar phur pa'i lha zhe gnyis dgod do //
NK019(dza)001:6799: zhes khrag 'thung rol pa dang sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor gnyis so sor phye ste /
NK019(dza)001:6800: phyi ma la rdo rje gzhon nu khro bcu yab
NK019(dza)001:6801: yum khra thabs nyi shu dang bcas gsungs pas na
NK019(dza)001:6802: / da lta'i dbang tsaka rnams su bsrung 'khor gyi khro bcu yab yum tsam las mi 'byung yang /
NK019(dza)001:6803: khra thabs nyi shu bsnan dgos par mngon zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6804: he ru ka 'dus pa las kyang /
NK019(dza)001:6805: phyi rol khro bcu yab yum ste //
NK019(dza)001:6806: phra men nyi shu yang sprul dag /
NK019(dza)001:6807: bye ba phrag ni sa ya 'phro //
NK019(dza)001:6809: gsum pa bsgrub pa'i yan lag sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bskur ba la /
NK019(dza)001:6810: gang du bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK019(dza)001:6811: gang bskur bya'i dbang gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6814: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la //
NK019(dza)001:6815: sgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bya //
NK019(dza)001:6816: zhes pas sgrub dbang gang du bskur ba a nu yo ga'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK019(dza)001:6817: tshogs chen 'dus pa thun mong ma yin pa'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK019(dza)001:6818: rtsa rgyud du de'i sgrub lugs kyi le'u las gsungs
NK019(dza)001:6819: pa dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor zhes
NK019(dza)001:6820: bya ba de nyid yin pas /
NK019(dza)001:6821: de bshad pa la drug ste /
NK019(dza)001:6826: nub tha mar slob dpon 'jug cing dngos grub blang ba /
NK019(dza)001:6827: slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6830: de nas sgrub dbang grags chu'i dus //
NK019(dza)001:6831: phyi nang bar mtshams nang dang 'dra //
NK019(dza)001:6832: gshin rje'i rgyal po'i sgo byang bya //
NK019(dza)001:6833: phrin las bcol te bar mtshams bcad //
NK019(dza)001:6835: nang dbang dang sgrub dbang gnyis dgos dbang gis dus tshigs so sor bcad nas bskur ba'i tshe /
NK019(dza)001:6836: phyi mtshams rgyal tho dang phyogs skyong gi tho sdom zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6837: bar mtshams phyogs skyong phur gdab dang dam sri gnon pa'ang sger du bya dgos mod /
NK019(dza)001:6838: 'dir bsnyen sgrub bzhi stan thog gcig tu byed pa'i lugs ltar na /
NK019(dza)001:6839: phyi mtshams kyi tho gnyis po gso zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6841: mtshams phur la phrin las bskul ba dang /
NK019(dza)001:6842: dam sri sngar mnan zin gyi steng du bros gzir /
NK019(dza)001:6843: khyad par 'dir gshin rje'i rgyal po'i sgo byang 'dogs pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6844: nang mtshams 'bar ba lta ba'i mtshams sogs bzhi nang dbang gi dus dang 'dra bar bcad do //
NK019(dza)001:6847: gnas dang 'khor dang yo byad brlab //
NK019(dza)001:6848: ces pas ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis sngar ltar byin gyis brlab pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6851: go ma ye btang thig g.yog brlab //
NK019(dza)001:6852: rang bzhin ting 'dzin gzugs brnyan thig /
NK019(dza)001:6853: tshon bkye phyag rgya mar me dgod //
NK019(dza)001:6854: mchod pa'i bye brag tshang bar dgram //
NK019(dza)001:6855: dur khrod gsang ba'i lugs su bzhengs //
NK019(dza)001:6857: stegs bur bdud rtsi lngas go ma ye btang la thig g.yog brlabs te /
NK019(dza)001:6858: steng gi nam mkha' rang bzhin ye shes kyi thig dang /
NK019(dza)001:6859: 'og tu sa gzhi la gzugs brnyan las kyi thig cho ga bzhin du gdab cing /
NK019(dza)001:6860: thig ji ltar btab pa'i gzhi la tshon rim par
NK019(dza)001:6861: bkye bas rtsa rgyud kyi tshogs chen 'dus pa'i sgrub
NK019(dza)001:6863: 'og khang khro bo'i dkyil 'khor lte ba re'u mig
NK019(dza)001:6864: dgu pa'i phyi rol 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa drug
NK019(dza)001:6865: rim gru chad dang bcas pa'i mthar khyams gru bzhi
NK019(dza)001:6866: rim pa lngas bskor ba'i nang ma bzhi'i phyogs rer
NK019(dza)001:6867: sgo sgo khyud can rgyan med gnyis gnyis te brgyad
NK019(dza)001:6868: dang / khyams lnga pa la sgo rgyan rta babs sogs kyis brgyan pa'i sgo gcig ste /
NK019(dza)001:6869: sgo dgu pa'i dkyil 'khor dur khrod gsang ba'i lugs su bzhengs shing /
NK019(dza)001:6870: steng khang zhi dkyil nang dbang gi skabs dang 'dra
NK019(dza)001:6871: ba sbrel ba'i zhi khro brtsegs ma'i dkyil 'khor bris
NK019(dza)001:6872: la / bgegs bskrad de mtshan ma byin gyis brlabs nas sku rten sogs phyag rgya'i rnam pa /
NK019(dza)001:6873: sgrub rten mar me sogs sgrub dbang gi rdzas /
NK019(dza)001:6874: mchod pa'i yo byad dang dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan rnams tshul bzhin du dgod pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6875: bzhi pa la sbyor dngos gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:6876: sbyor ba sgrub pa'i 'go 'dzin pa'i las phreng na /
NK019(dza)001:6878: gsang sgo phye la brda phyag 'tshal //
NK019(dza)001:6879: rtags gdab rgyan gyis legs par brgyan //
NK019(dza)001:6880: byin dbab phyag 'tshal dam yang bca' //
NK019(dza)001:6881: dngos grub gsol zhing bskang dang bshags //
NK019(dza)001:6882: las kyi phreng ba rdzogs byas te //
NK019(dza)001:6883: zhes pas brda sgo phye la brda phyag 'tshal /
NK019(dza)001:6884: dpon slob thams cad la rtags gdab cing /
NK019(dza)001:6885: gos rgyan bzang po bstar te dkyil 'khor la byin dbab /
NK019(dza)001:6886: gral phyag dang tshul phyag byas te stan la 'dug nas /
NK019(dza)001:6887: dam bca' dang dngos grub gsol zhing bskang bshags bya ba rnams so //
NK019(dza)001:6888: dngos gzhi las gzhung bsrang ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6890: ting 'dzin bskyed dang rang bzhin drangs //
NK019(dza)001:6891: gnyis med mchod pa rim bzhin 'bul //
NK019(dza)001:6892: bzlas brjod bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi bsrang //
NK019(dza)001:6893: stong tshigs rkang thon mchod pa bya //
NK019(dza)001:6894: dus drug las phreng tshogs mchod snyeg /
NK019(dza)001:6895: dus drug bskang gso'i cho ga bya //
NK019(dza)001:6896: dus drug bar gcod nyul le bzlog /
NK019(dza)001:6897: ces pas sgrub pa zhag grangs ji tsam byed pa'i dkyil 'khor zhag gi chog khrigs te /
NK019(dza)001:6898: las kyi dbu drang ba sogs las gzhung gi sngon 'gro ji ltar rigs pa sngon du 'gro bas /
NK019(dza)001:6899: dngos gzhi nyin mtshan dus drug tu /
NK019(dza)001:6900: zhi khro'i dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed pa /
NK019(dza)001:6901: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drang ba /
NK019(dza)001:6902: dam ye gnyis med du byas pa la mchod pa /
NK019(dza)001:6903: dzapa khang phye ste gsal ba gsum gyis dzapa bzlas bya ba ste /
NK019(dza)001:6904: las kyi rim pa rnam pa bzhis bsnyen sgrub kyi gzhung bsrang /
NK019(dza)001:6905: thun mthar lha'i rkang thon du stong tshigs kyis mchod cing bstod /
NK019(dza)001:6908: nyul le 'dul ba rnams kyang thun drug ka'i mjug tu bya ba yin no //
NK019(dza)001:6911: zhag bdun tha mar slob dpon 'jug /
NK019(dza)001:6912: dngos grub rnam bzhi rim gyis blang //
NK019(dza)001:6913: dzapa skor dang pos thugs dam bskul //
NK019(dza)001:6914: bar du sbyin sreg mchod pa bya //
NK019(dza)001:6915: tha ma gnad la dbab pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:6916: gshegs shing gsol byang bstim par bya //
NK019(dza)001:6917: zhes pas sgrub zhag bdun rdzogs pa'i tha ma la
NK019(dza)001:6918: slob dpon bdag nyid dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas lha
NK019(dza)001:6919: dang rdzas las dngos grub blang ste /
NK019(dza)001:6920: de la lha las blang ba la bzhi las /
NK019(dza)001:6921: dang po dngos grub bskul ba'i dzapa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6923: mdun bskyed las dngos grub kyi 'od zer tshur bsdus
NK019(dza)001:6924: te bdag la bstim pa kho nas dzapa bzla ba'o
NK019(dza)001:6926: bsgrub bya'i dngos grub spel ba'am dbang du bya ba'i
NK019(dza)001:6927: phyir rgyas pa dang dbang gang rigs kyi sreg blugs
NK019(dza)001:6928: 'bul ba'o // gsum pa gnad la dbab pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6930: dngos grub bskul ba'i rim pa rnams //
NK019(dza)001:6931: spyir bskul ba dang gnad nas bskul //
NK019(dza)001:6932: nye bar bskul ba'i rim pa yin //
NK019(dza)001:6933: zhes pas sgrub khog tu bkod pa ltar spyir bskul ba /
NK019(dza)001:6935: nye bar bskul ba rnams te /
NK019(dza)001:6936: 'di'i spyi dang gnad nas bskul ba gnyis kyi gyer
NK019(dza)001:6937: tshig go barjesa na 'thad dam snyam pa kho bo'i
NK019(dza)001:6938: rnam rtog go // bzhi pa gshegs shing gsol byang byas la bstim pa ni /
NK019(dza)001:6941: sregs ston gsum phyag bzhes mi mthun pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6942: 'dir glan chen po rdo rje 'od sregs ston gyi lugs su mdzad pa ltar /
NK019(dza)001:6943: zhi khro steng 'og 'ju 'dul gyi tshul gyis khro dkyil las gsal shing gi dngos grub len pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:6944: de nas rdzas las dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6946: me tog 'thor dang bdud rtsi yi //
NK019(dza)001:6947: dngos grub blang ba tshul bzhin bya //
NK019(dza)001:6948: bkra shis zas tshe'i dngos grub ni //
NK019(dza)001:6949: zla gam dbang gi gzhal yang nas //
NK019(dza)001:6950: bkra shis brjod dang cha lngar bgo //
NK019(dza)001:6951: ru lu'i brjod pa ma lus bya //
NK019(dza)001:6952: zhes pas dkyil 'khor la me tog dor nas sman gyi dngos grub blang /
NK019(dza)001:6955: bkra shis kyi rdzas rnams las dngos grub blang zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6956: shis pa brjod pas brtan par bya ba rnams so //
NK019(dza)001:6957: rjes chog gi rdzas cha lngar bgo ba sogs dbang gi mthar bya zhing /
NK019(dza)001:6958: ru lu'i dzapa bro lha rje glan dbang gi rjes dang /
NK019(dza)001:6959: rtsi lung pa 'dir mdzad ces 'gos kyi las thor bshad do //
NK019(dza)001:6962: yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i sems //
NK019(dza)001:6963: lha dang dbyer med gyur pa yi //
NK019(dza)001:6964: slob dpon grub thob bzhugs pa des //
NK019(dza)001:6965: bu rnams gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor bcug /
NK019(dza)001:6966: ces pas sgrub chen gyi 'gangs che shos dngos grub yum gyi mkha' las blang ba yin pas /
NK019(dza)001:6967: slob dpon gyis rang don du yab yum rjes chags kyi sbyor ba'i nye rgyus dngos grub blangs rjes /
NK019(dza)001:6968: gzhan don slob bu rnams thabs shes rol pa'i 'od
NK019(dza)001:6969: zer gyis zhal du bcug pa mkha' nang du sbyangs
NK019(dza)001:6970: te lhar byas pas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du gzhug
NK019(dza)001:6971: pa'o // gnyis pa gang bskur bya'i dbang ni /
NK019(dza)001:6973: sgrub dbang bcu gsum las kyis bskur //
NK019(dza)001:6974: grags pa'i chu bo'i las tho'o //
NK019(dza)001:6976: de la sgrub dbang rtsa ba bcu gsum ni /
NK019(dza)001:6977: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK019(dza)001:6978: de dag kun la spyod sgrub pa'i //
NK019(dza)001:6979: sgrub pa'i dbang rnams bskur bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:6980: dang po shes rab rig pa'i sems lon gtan tshigs byin //
NK019(dza)001:6981: gnyis pa snying rje rtags dbang nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor byin //
NK019(dza)001:6982: gsum pa 'gro don rdzogs pa'i thong gshol 'bar ba byin //
NK019(dza)001:6983: bzhi pa dug gsum sprugs pa ga'u rnam gsum byin //
NK019(dza)001:6984: lnga pa srid gsum sgrol ba'i ka tar mtshon cha byin //
NK019(dza)001:6985: drug pa skyon gyis ma gos rnam dag pad+ma byin //
NK019(dza)001:6986: bdun pa las rnams rdzogs pa'i ti ra'i dbyug pa byin //
NK019(dza)001:6987: brgyad pa gnyis med 'khril ba sbrul nag chun po byin //
NK019(dza)001:6988: dgu pa gsang ba shes rab lha mo'o //
NK019(dza)001:6989: bcu pa kun la dbang ba'i 'dod yon sna lnga byin //
NK019(dza)001:6990: bcu gcig sgrub pa'i rgyal po dkyil 'khor gtso bo byin //
NK019(dza)001:6991: bcu gnyis thams cad sgrub pa'i sgrub rdzas thams cad byin //
NK019(dza)001:6992: bcu gsum gnyis su med pa 'i thig le ming gi dbang //
NK019(dza)001:6994: de las yan lag brgya dang bco lngar dbye ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:6995: sngon gyi slob dpon rnams kyis slob ma thun mong
NK019(dza)001:6996: ba rnams phyi dang nang gi chu bo gnyis kyis
NK019(dza)001:6998: sgrub gsang gi chu bo gnyis dus tshigs re bar
NK019(dza)001:6999: du bcug nas slob ma khyad par ba rnams la
NK019(dza)001:7000: logs su mdzad srol byung ba ltar /
NK019(dza)001:7001: thun mong pa'i ngor dpe mkhyud kyis dbang don rgya
NK019(dza)001:7002: cher 'byed pa'i yig rgyun rnams la'ang mang nyung dang
NK019(dza)001:7003: tshig mi 'dra ba ci rigs snang bas /
NK019(dza)001:7004: 'dir dbye tshul mkhas grub g.yung ston rdo rje dpal gyis mdzad pa'i rnam bshad du /
NK019(dza)001:7005: bzhi pa ga'u'i dbang la gsum /
NK019(dza)001:7006: lnga pa mtshon cha'i dbang la drug /
NK019(dza)001:7007: bcu pa 'dod yon gyi dbang la lnga /
NK019(dza)001:7008: bcu gcig pa sgrub pa'i rgyal po'i dbang la lnga /
NK019(dza)001:7009: bcu gnyis pa sgrub rdzas thams cad kyi dbang la brgyad cu gya brgyad rnams dang /
NK019(dza)001:7010: lhag ma brgyad po la re re ste /
NK019(dza)001:7011: khyon dril bas yan lag brgya dang bco lnga yod par gsungs pa las /
NK019(dza)001:7012: sgrub rdzas thams cad kyi dbang gi skabs 'dir /
NK019(dza)001:7013: sgrol chen bsam grub rdo rje'i phyag bris kyi dbang don rgya cher 'byed par /
NK019(dza)001:7014: bcu gnyis sgrub rdzas kun gyi dbang bskur la //
NK019(dza)001:7015: yang dag dur khrod brdal dang phur bu rdzas //
NK019(dza)001:7016: bdud rtsi pho brang bde chen dbang bskur ro //
NK019(dza)001:7018: gro ston dpal ldan grags kyi phyag dper /
NK019(dza)001:7019: bcu gcig bcu gnyis sgrub pa'i rim pa la //
NK019(dza)001:7020: rdo rje tshe dang thugs sgrub sman la sogs //
NK019(dza)001:7021: 'das dang 'jig rten sgrub pa ma lus pa'i //
NK019(dza)001:7022: gtso dang sgrub thabs thams cad bskur bar bya //
NK019(dza)001:7023: bye brag brjod na bsam 'das brjod mi lang //
NK019(dza)001:7026: rdo rje tshe dang sman la sogs //
NK019(dza)001:7027: sgrub pa ma lus sgrub shig ces //
NK019(dza)001:7028: sgrub rdzas thams cad byin par bya //
NK019(dza)001:7029: zhes pa'i skabs kyi mchan yol dge bsnyen gyi phyag bris mar /
NK019(dza)001:7030: yang phur bdud rtsi sogs kyis dbang ste rjes su gnang ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:7031: zhes pa tsam las mi 'byung yang /
NK019(dza)001:7032: zur ham lcam sring nas brgyud pa'i dbang chog lugs
NK019(dza)001:7033: gnyis la gcig tu chad pa'i rgyun cig shos kyis
NK019(dza)001:7035: da lta'i phyag bzhes kyi dbang chog ltar brtsis na /
NK019(dza)001:7036: 'dren pa'i las byang chung ngus bskur ba'i sgrub rdzas thun mong pa bco lnga /
NK019(dza)001:7037: thun mong ma yin pa'i sgrub rdzas rol pa'i chas bcu /
NK019(dza)001:7038: khyad par gyi sgrub rdzas la spyi dang bye brag gnyis las /
NK019(dza)001:7044: bkra shis gtsang ma'i bam dang /
NK019(dza)001:7045: dag pa lha'i rdzas kyi bam /
NK019(dza)001:7049: phur bu bzhi po re re'ang bzhi bzhi ste bcu drug /
NK019(dza)001:7059: bye brag gi sgrub rdzas la /
NK019(dza)001:7060: gshin rje gshed kyi sgo byang /
NK019(dza)001:7064: rdo rje gzhon nu'i bsnyen phur dang /
NK019(dza)001:7065: mtshams phur rnams so sor brtsis pas bcu /
NK019(dza)001:7070: drag sngags kyi zhi rgyas dbang drag gi ho ma ste bzhi /
NK019(dza)001:7079: tshe chang rnams te dril bas brgyad cu gya brgyad do //
NK019(dza)001:7080: de ltar bye brag sgrub sde'i sgrub rdzas kyi dbang kyang skabs 'dir bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:7086: yang dag thugs dang bdud rtsi phur //
NK019(dza)001:7087: ma mo mchod bstod drag sngags rnams //
NK019(dza)001:7088: cha rkyen yin phyir rig 'dzin brgyad //
NK019(dza)001:7089: tshe ni spyi yi kha skong yin //
NK019(dza)001:7090: sgo byang phyi nang dgra bgegs skrod //
NK019(dza)001:7091: rdzas skongs mar me bdud rtsi sman //
NK019(dza)001:7092: mtshams phur gdab kha bsnyen phur rten //
NK019(dza)001:7093: ma chen rak+tasa thugs dam bskangs //
NK019(dza)001:7094: 'jig rten mchod rten drag zor gtor //
NK019(dza)001:7095: rig 'dzin gtor phud tshe zan rdzas //
NK019(dza)001:7097: bzhi pa sgrub chen gyi yan lag gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bo bskur ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:7099: rdzogs pa a ti yo ga la //
NK019(dza)001:7100: gsang dbang rdzogs pa'i chu bos bya //
NK019(dza)001:7103: dbang don rnam par 'byed pa las /
NK019(dza)001:7104: sgrub dbang bcu gsum rdzoogs pa dang //
NK019(dza)001:7105: gsang ba kun gyi bdag yin pas //
NK019(dza)001:7106: dkar dmar 'dres pa'i byang chub sems //
NK019(dza)001:7107: dbang thob de yi lce la bzhag /
NK019(dza)001:7108: gnyis med don dam byang chub sems //
NK019(dza)001:7109: dbang thob de yi sems la bzhag /
NK019(dza)001:7112: rdo rje slob dpon yab yum sbyor //
NK019(dza)001:7113: dkar dmar 'dre pa'i byang chub sems //
NK019(dza)001:7114: bu mchog de yi lce la bzhag /
NK019(dza)001:7115: don dam byang chub sems chen po /
NK019(dza)001:7116: bu mchog de yi snying la bzhag /
NK019(dza)001:7117: rdzogs pa'i chu bo'i las tho'o //
NK019(dza)001:7118: zhes pas kun rdzob byang sems dang /
NK019(dza)001:7119: don dam byang sems kyi dbang gnyis su dbye ba las /
NK019(dza)001:7120: yan lag gzhan spro ru med de //
NK019(dza)001:7121: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa las //
NK019(dza)001:7122: bzhi pa gsang ba'i dbang chu du mar spro ru med //
NK019(dza)001:7124: de la dang po kun rdzob byang sems kyi dbang lus la bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK019(dza)001:7126: rdo rje slob dpon yab yum sbyor //
NK019(dza)001:7127: zhes pa ni gsang dbang gi khongs su sher dbang
NK019(dza)001:7128: sbas pas bla ma'i man ngag la ltos dgos pa'i
NK019(dza)001:7130: gsang dbang la bla ma yab yum gyi lus dkyil dang /
NK019(dza)001:7131: sher dbang la phyag rgya ma'i mkha' gsang gi dkyil 'khor gnyis 'jug bya'i dkyil 'khor yin la /
NK019(dza)001:7132: de mtshon byed brda'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK019(dza)001:7133: gsang rdzas kyi bdud rtsi dang /
NK019(dza)001:7134: me long gi dkyil 'khor gnyis kyis mtshon par bya ba yin no //
NK019(dza)001:7138: gsang dbang ni bla ma yab yum mnyam par sbyor
NK019(dza)001:7139: ba'i byang chub kyi sems bu'i lce la bzhag nas
NK019(dza)001:7140: bskur zhing / sher dbang ni slob bu nyid shes
NK019(dza)001:7141: rab ma dang snyoms par zhugs pa'i khu rdul gsang
NK019(dza)001:7142: rtsa phan tshun du ltems pa yab kyi gsang ba
NK019(dza)001:7143: rdo rje'i lce la bzhag nas bskur bas 'byung ldog
NK019(dza)001:7144: gi dga' ba bzhi la ngo sprod pa'o //
NK019(dza)001:7145: gnyis pa don dam byang sems kyi dbang sems la bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor ni /
NK019(dza)001:7146: mtshon bya sems nyid dkyil 'khor rnam gsum ma 'dres yongs rdzogs su gnas pa nyid yin la /
NK019(dza)001:7147: de yang dbyings dang ye shes zung du 'jug pa ste /
NK019(dza)001:7148: de'i ye shes kyi rtsal snang tshogs brgyad dang /
NK019(dza)001:7149: dbyings kyi rtsal snang yul brgyad de /
NK019(dza)001:7150: bcu drug po'ang dbyings dang ye shes su 'du ba'i phyir /
NK019(dza)001:7151: de mtshon byed tsit+ta rin po che'i dkyil 'khor la rtsa ba dbyings ye shes gnyis dang /
NK019(dza)001:7152: de gnyis kyi rtsal yul yul can bcu drug mtshon
NK019(dza)001:7153: pa'i a yig bco brgyad kyi rnam pa bkod pa
NK019(dza)001:7154: nyid yin pas / mtshon byed kyi brda' de la
NK019(dza)001:7155: brten nas mtshon bya don dam byang chub sems kyi
NK019(dza)001:7156: dkyil 'khor du bya rtsol med pa'i shes rab kyis
NK019(dza)001:7157: nyid yin pas / zhugs te / ye ji bzhin pa'i gnas lugs rtogs pa'i don de nyid /
NK019(dza)001:7158: rnam par snang mdzad thig le dbang gi tan+t+ra las
NK019(dza)001:7159: phyung ba lta ba ye 'byams kyi dbang le dang
NK019(dza)001:7160: / yongs su grub pa'i dbang le gnyis kyis nges shes bskyed cing /
NK019(dza)001:7161: kun bzang thugs kyi gdams les gsang gnyer gtod pa'i tshul gyis rig pa'i rtsal dbang bskur ba'o //
NK019(dza)001:7162: de ltar yan lag dang yan lag can rtsa ba'i
NK019(dza)001:7163: dkyil 'khor rnams su rtsa ba'i dbang chu bo bzhis
NK019(dza)001:7164: bsdus pa sum cu rtsa drug las yan lag rags
NK019(dza)001:7165: pa brgyad brgya so gcig tu phye nas bskur tshul
NK019(dza)001:7166: 'di ni / sbyangs pas snod du gyur pa'i slob
NK019(dza)001:7167: ma la mdo yongs rdzogs kyi dkyil 'khor du theg
NK019(dza)001:7168: pa thams cad 'dus pa'i mdo dbang bskur tshul slob
NK019(dza)001:7169: dpon bde ba gsal mdzad kyi las thos bkral ba'i
NK019(dza)001:7171: 'dir yan lag brgyad brgya so gcig la rags pa zhes zer ba ni /
NK019(dza)001:7172: dbang don rgya cher 'byed pa las /
